====Usage notes====
When expressing action in progress, 呢 can be used with {{zh-l|正在}} and {{zh-l|著/著}} in a sentence. This is the full patern. Each part is optional.
: {{zh-usex|我們 '''正在''' 上 '''著''' 漢語 課 '''呢'''。|We '''are''' attend'''ing''' a Chinese lesson|link=y|in_notes=y}}

